<br />

<br />
ATM I am level 19 and have a routine of capping my melee skills then kiting my way to the next level.  I am worried that my leveling will really slow down after the patch and am considering abandoning my melee skills and leveling up as much as possible before the nerf.
<br />
I know that I will have a hard job getting my skills back up afterwards, but would rather do this than grind my way through levels in the same manner I have done with every other class I have played.
<br />
Is this the right thing to do? Or will I regret it?</span></td>
